  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, org.apache.ignite.compute.ComputeTask<java.util.List<java.lang.Long>,java.lang.Boolean>

    public class CrossOverTask
extends org.apache.ignite.compute.ComputeTaskAdapter<java.util.List<java.lang.Long>,java.lang.Boolean>
    Responsible for assigning 2 X 'parent' chromosomes to produce 2 X 'child' chromosomes. CrossOverTask leverages Ignite's data affinity capabilities for routing CrossOverJobs to primary IgniteNode where 'parent' chromosomes reside.
